    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The attribute or quality of an object reflecting light to a significant degree, and either giving back an image or reflection, for example as in mirrors, or more diffusely, for example as in desert sand.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
